    "text": "Colfax Street, east side, north of Murdock Ave. (an extension of One Hundred Fourteenth Ave.), showing the H. E. Remsen farmhouse of 1873. G. H. Remsen was the owner in 1891. It was still his property in 1918. This is a set of two views, of which, No. 2 shows a private lane from Colfax Street leading to the house.\n\nApril 1925.\n\nEugene L. Armbruster Collection.\n",
